<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A KAN CAWMTU</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa nih, a mi hna, a kan philh, ballo
 Kan vansan, caan poh ah, a kan bomh
 Ttihhlah uh, phang hlah uh, kan Pathian a um
 Bochan tlak, Pathian nung, kan ngei.

[C1]
   A kan bawmtu, Bawipa, a kan cawmtu, Bawipa
   Kan ningzah, mualphonak, a kan huppheng
   A kan bawmtu, Bawipa, a kan cawmtu, Bawipa
   Hallelui-jah a men.

[V2]
 Lungretheih, le khuaruah-har in kan, um tawn
 Van a sang, lei a pit, lung a dong
 Sihmanhseh, Bawipa lei, kan panhtthan, tikah
 Lunglawmhnak, khua a ceu, tthantawn.

[V3]
 Chaw le va, ei le din, kan hruk ding, hni puan
 Kan herhmi, thil vialte, a kan pek
 A kan bawm-tu le a, kan cawmtu, Bawipa
 Zungzal in, kan sinah, a um.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
</song>